{"id":14416,"date":"2023-11-16T18:26:34","date_gmt":"2023-11-16T11:26:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?p=14416"},"modified":"2023-11-22T16:55:47","modified_gmt":"2023-11-22T09:55:47","slug":"mung-nam-moi-tai-reflections","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/mung-nam-moi-tai-reflections\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u1eebng n\u0103m m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Reflections"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47ka1tcc fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/New-Year-5course-header.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/410a4691ad6c5eb267caddf4e1ce589e_New-Year-5course-header-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/410a4691ad6c5eb267caddf4e1ce589e_New-Year-5course-header-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/410a4691ad6c5eb267caddf4e1ce589e_New-Year-5course-header-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/410a4691ad6c5eb267caddf4e1ce589e_New-Year-5course-header-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/New-Year-5course-header.jpg\" alt=\"New-Year-5course-header\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-47lked41 fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-47lked42 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47lked46 fg-image  img-responsive fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/2920c7f2b4464a229d189ea6bcb3abf9_Reflections-Restaurant-Logo-PNG-300-c-90.png\" alt=\"Reflections Restaurant Logo-PNG\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-5dvno8tp fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">N&Acirc;NG LY CH&Uacute;C M\u1eeaNG N\u0102M M\u1edaI&nbsp;<\/h3>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 134px;top: 37.375px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-68h42uts fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">C&ugrave;ng n&acirc;ng ly ch&uacute;c m\u1eebng n\u0103m m\u1edbi v\u1edbi b&aacute;nh canape v&agrave; r\u01b0\u1ee3u s&acirc;m panh s\u1ee7i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c 6 m&oacute;n \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c cao c\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i tr&ecirc;n n\u1ec1n giai \u0111i\u1ec7u piano du d\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u0129a H\u1ea3i s\u1ea3n, n\u01a1i nh\u1eefng nguy&ecirc;n li\u1ec7u t\u01b0\u01a1i ngon nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y m\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt. Th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u01b0\u1ee3t m&agrave; v&agrave; s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m&oacute;n Foie Gras Terrine v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ed1t Truffle, m\u1ed9t ki\u1ec7t t&aacute;c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. H&atilde;y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecb m&ecirc; ho\u1eb7c b\u1edfi m&oacute;n T&ocirc;m h&ugrave;m Ravioli h\u1ea3o h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi Caviar &amp; Uni, C&aacute; tuy\u1ebft, v&agrave; sau \u0111&oacute; l&agrave; Th\u1ecbt b&ecirc; n\u01b0\u1edbng, tuy\u1ec7t t&aacute;c \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c to&aacute;t l&ecirc;n s\u1ef1 phong ph&uacute; v&ocirc; song. Cu\u1ed1i c&ugrave;ng, h&atilde;y \u0111\u1eafm m&igrave;nh trong b\u1ea3n giao h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ea7y m&ecirc; ho\u1eb7c c\u1ee7a m&oacute;n tr&aacute;ng mi\u1ec7ng khi m&oacute;n Poached Pear v&agrave; Mignardise \u0111\u1eadm \u0111&agrave;, m&ecirc; ho\u1eb7c c&aacute;c gi&aacute;c quan c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1eb1ng v\u1ecb ng\u1ecdt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a n&oacute;.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">H&atilde;y s\u1eb5n s&agrave;ng \u0111&oacute;n ch&agrave;o n\u0103m 2024 t\u1ea1i nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng Reflections.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-68h438n3 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n 6 m&oacute;n \u0111&ecirc;m giao th\u1eeba ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb \u200b\u200b<strong>3.090.000++ VN\u0110<\/strong>\/kh&aacute;ch&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* N&acirc;ng t\u1ea7m tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang ch\u1ec9 <strong>1.690.000++ VN\u0110<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng&agrave;y 31\/12\/2023, 17:30 &ndash; 22:00<\/p>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 589px;top: 18.1875px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5fjrv0 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-3 fg-text-dark\"><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5fk27s fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-3 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5flgsa buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Reflections_New-Year-menu.pdf\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">XEM TH\u1ef0C \u0110\u01a0N<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5fk0l6 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-3 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5flf8r buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tablecheck.com\/en\/shops\/reflections-restaurant\/reserve\" class=\"ffb-block-button-2-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">\u0110\u1eb6T B\u00c0N<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5fk3ks fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-3 fg-text-da